reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for a cruise
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for a cruise. Worked perfectly. The longer cord reached from the vanity to the bed area for phone and tablet charging. Was easy to move out of the way during the day. Small-ish size fit well in my luggage. I totally recomm nd this for when you don’t need a surge protector or cannot have one (cruise ships).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Every feature is a plus!
reviews.reviewText: This little guy is a keeper. The desk footprint is minimal, the configuration of the outlets is compact but doesn't crowd the plugs, and the way it wraps for storage or travel is a dream. Three outlets and a port -- what you need on the go, not at your desk or in your office. The icing on the cake for me is the flat wall plug and five foot cord, again, space saving and just enough. Get at least two, you will want one in your work bag and one in your overnight travel case at all times. And the kids will steal it.Recommended!
